                                              long testId,
                                              java.lang.Boolean omUser,
                                              java.lang.Boolean omAdmin,
                                              boolean sorted)
                                       throws ServiceException
Parameters:
operation - Operation
testId - Test identifier
omUser - Filtering by users allowed to do test (true) or not (false) or non filtering (null)
omAdmin - Filtering by users with administration privileges for the test (true) or not (false) or non filtering (null)
sorted - Flag to indicate if we want the results sorted by test and user
Returns:
